stub instead, otherwise hsc2hs panics at compile-time.

commit.message:
Win32: Hide console primitives from Win32-2.9 (#145)

Win32 provides a few console primitives as of the 2.9 release, resulting
in name shadowing warnings with our own local versions. Hide those from
Win32 to avoid the warnings.
